{"video_id": "AOpqOuoNX0w", "title": "Daily Evening Bhagavatam Discourse | HH Stoka Krishna Swami | SB 1.6.19-20 | 15-11-2021", "speaker": "HH Stoka Krishna Swami", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AOpqOuoNX0w", "duration": 1079, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 13.780000000000001, "text": " ओम अज्ञानति मिरान्धस्य ज्ञानान्जनिषलाकया चक्षुरुन्मीलितं येनतस्मैश्री गुरवेनमहा नमा ओम विष्णु पादाया कृष्ण प्रेष्ठाय भूतले"}, {"start": 13.780000000000001, "end": 28.520000000000003, "text": " श्रीमते भक्ति वेदांत स्वामिन्नितिनामिने नमस्ते सारस्वते देवे गौरवाणी प्रचारिने निर्विशेशा शुन्यवादी पाश्चात्यदेशतारिने"}, {"start": 28.52, "end": 48.019999999999996, "text": " जय श्री कृष्ण चैतन्या प्रभू नित्यानन्द, श्री अद्वैत गदाधर, श्रीवास अधीगवर भक्त वृन्द, हरे कृष्ण, हरे कृष्ण, कृष्ण कृष्ण, हरे हरे, हरे राम, हरे राम, राम राम, हरे हरे,"}, {"start": 48.02, "end": 62.18000000000001, "text": " OM NAMO BHAGVATE VASUDEVAYA NARAYANAM NAMASKRITYA NARAM CHAIVANAROTTAMAM DEVIM SARASVATHIM VYASAM TATO JAYAM UDIRAYET"}, {"start": 62.18000000000001, "end": 74.52000000000001, "text": " In this session we will be discussing from the first canto, sixth chapter, nineteenth and twentieth verses of the Srimad Bhagavatam."}, {"start": 74.52, "end": 89.75999999999999, "text": " First the nineteenth verse, DIDRUKSHU STAD AHAM BHUYAH, PRANIDHAYA MANOHRDI, VIKSHAM ANO PINAPASYAM, AVITRUPTA IVATURAHA."}, {"start": 90.75999999999999, "end": 98.3, "text": " The meaning of this verse is, I desire to see again that transcendental form of the Lord,"}, {"start": 99.3, "end": 103.75999999999999, "text": " but despite my attempts to concentrate upon the heart with eagerness,"}, {"start": 103.76, "end": 115.42, "text": " to view the form again, I could not see him anymore, and thus, dissatisfied, I was very much aggrieved."}, {"start": 118.16000000000001, "end": 133.12, "text": " So the background for this verse is, in the previous session, we had heard how Narad Muni began to meditate on the form of the Lord in the heart."}, {"start": 133.76, "end": 140.66, "text": " As he had been taught by the Bhaktivedantas, and using his intelligence to search out for the Lord in the heart,"}, {"start": 142.06, "end": 148.95999999999998, "text": " and very quickly he came to the stage of bhava, tears started flowing down from his eyes,"}, {"start": 150.39999999999998, "end": 157.2, "text": " and every part of his body he felt separately enlivened."}, {"start": 158.56, "end": 163.51999999999998, "text": " In that state, the Lord gave him darshan within the heart,"}, {"start": 163.76, "end": 176.79999999999998, "text": " a brief darshan, but after a brief moment, when he was in the experiencing that ecstasy of joy of seeing the form of the Lord in the heart,"}, {"start": 178.14, "end": 180.35999999999999, "text": " suddenly he lost sight of that form."}, {"start": 182.5, "end": 190.89999999999998, "text": " Then, he again tried to see that form of the Lord."}, {"start": 191.6, "end": 193.35999999999999, "text": " So that is the description here."}, {"start": 193.76, "end": 199.48, "text": " I desire to see again that transcendental form of the Lord in the heart,"}, {"start": 200.0, "end": 206.85999999999999, "text": " but despite my attempts to concentrate upon the heart, with eagerness to view the form again."}, {"start": 208.35999999999999, "end": 209.94, "text": " He is again wanting to see."}, {"start": 210.6, "end": 213.92, "text": " So he is thinking, let me do the same thing which I did previously."}, {"start": 215.14, "end": 217.98, "text": " But he could not see the Lord,"}, {"start": 217.98, "end": 222.98, "text": " in spite of very..."}, {"start": 223.76, "end": 225.76, "text": " sincere attempts,"}, {"start": 225.76, "end": 227.57999999999998, "text": " the same way,"}, {"start": 227.57999999999998, "end": 235.06, "text": " exactly the same way, as he had been taught, as he had done already, as he had already seen, he could not again"}, {"start": 235.64, "end": 237.64, "text": " see the form of the Lord, and"}, {"start": 238.98, "end": 240.98, "text": " he was very much"}, {"start": 241.92, "end": 243.92, "text": " dissatisfied and"}, {"start": 243.92, "end": 245.92, "text": " became agreed."}, {"start": 248.0, "end": 251.44, "text": " So, Srila Prabhupada explains in the purport that"}, {"start": 253.76000000000002, "end": 259.76, "text": " there is no mechanical process"}, {"start": 259.76, "end": 261.76, "text": " to see the Lord,"}, {"start": 263.76, "end": 265.76, "text": " and"}, {"start": 265.76, "end": 267.76, "text": " it completely depends upon"}, {"start": 267.76, "end": 269.76, "text": " the"}, {"start": 269.76, "end": 271.76, "text": " causeless mercy of the Lord."}, {"start": 271.76, "end": 273.76, "text": " This word"}, {"start": 273.76, "end": 275.76, "text": " causeless means"}, {"start": 277.76, "end": 279.76, "text": " Lord will not give"}, {"start": 279.76, "end": 281.76, "text": " darshan because"}, {"start": 281.76, "end": 283.76, "text": " you are doing something good."}, {"start": 283.76, "end": 285.76, "text": " Because of"}, {"start": 285.76, "end": 287.76, "text": " some act of yours,"}, {"start": 287.76, "end": 289.76, "text": " as it generally happens"}, {"start": 289.76, "end": 291.76, "text": " in this material world,"}, {"start": 291.76, "end": 293.76, "text": " according to the laws of karma,"}, {"start": 293.76, "end": 295.76, "text": " I do some"}, {"start": 295.76, "end": 297.76, "text": " pious activity,"}, {"start": 297.76, "end": 299.76, "text": " I get some pious result,"}, {"start": 299.76, "end": 301.76, "text": " or I do some sinful activity,"}, {"start": 301.76, "end": 303.76, "text": " then I may get a"}, {"start": 303.76, "end": 305.76, "text": " sinful result."}, {"start": 305.76, "end": 307.76, "text": " But,"}, {"start": 307.76, "end": 309.76, "text": " the way to"}, {"start": 309.76, "end": 311.76, "text": " see the form of the Lord"}, {"start": 311.76, "end": 313.76, "text": " is no mechanical"}, {"start": 313.76, "end": 315.76, "text": " process, is no"}, {"start": 315.76, "end": 317.76, "text": " material"}, {"start": 317.76, "end": 319.76, "text": " method."}, {"start": 319.76, "end": 321.76, "text": " We are"}, {"start": 321.76, "end": 323.76, "text": " completely dependent"}, {"start": 323.76, "end": 325.76, "text": " upon the causeless"}, {"start": 325.76, "end": 327.76, "text": " mercy of the Lord in"}, {"start": 327.76, "end": 329.76, "text": " trying to see his form."}, {"start": 331.76, "end": 333.76, "text": " We cannot demand"}, {"start": 333.76, "end": 335.76, "text": " the Lord to be present before our vision."}, {"start": 335.76, "end": 337.76, "text": " That I did this,"}, {"start": 337.76, "end": 339.76, "text": " I followed the process,"}, {"start": 339.76, "end": 341.76, "text": " I had taken"}, {"start": 341.76, "end": 343.76, "text": " instructions from the"}, {"start": 343.76, "end": 345.76, "text": " masters,"}, {"start": 345.76, "end": 347.76, "text": " the bhaktivedantas,"}, {"start": 347.76, "end": 349.76, "text": " so I should be able to see."}, {"start": 349.76, "end": 351.76, "text": " Nobody can say that."}, {"start": 351.76, "end": 353.76, "text": " And"}, {"start": 353.76, "end": 355.76, "text": " Srila Prabhupada gives an example"}, {"start": 355.76, "end": 357.76, "text": " just as we"}, {"start": 357.76, "end": 359.76, "text": " cannot demand the sun"}, {"start": 359.76, "end": 361.76, "text": " to rise whenever"}, {"start": 361.76, "end": 363.76, "text": " we like."}, {"start": 363.76, "end": 365.76, "text": " Very good example."}, {"start": 365.76, "end": 367.76, "text": " The sun rises exactly"}, {"start": 367.76, "end": 369.76, "text": " at the time according to"}, {"start": 369.76, "end": 371.76, "text": " its own"}, {"start": 371.76, "end": 373.76, "text": " schedule."}, {"start": 373.76, "end": 375.76, "text": " The sun doesn't"}, {"start": 375.76, "end": 377.76, "text": " become subject to"}, {"start": 377.76, "end": 379.76, "text": " somebody else's control,"}, {"start": 379.76, "end": 381.76, "text": " or somebody else's"}, {"start": 381.76, "end": 383.76, "text": " demand. No."}, {"start": 383.76, "end": 385.76, "text": " Same way,"}, {"start": 385.76, "end": 387.76, "text": " the Supreme"}, {"start": 387.76, "end": 389.76, "text": " Lord will"}, {"start": 389.76, "end": 391.76, "text": " give darshan whenever"}, {"start": 391.76, "end": 393.76, "text": " he wills,"}, {"start": 393.76, "end": 395.76, "text": " whenever he wants to give darshan."}, {"start": 397.76, "end": 399.76, "text": " One should simply"}, {"start": 399.76, "end": 401.76, "text": " await the opportune moment"}, {"start": 401.76, "end": 403.76, "text": " and go on"}, {"start": 403.76, "end": 405.76, "text": " discharging his prescribed duty"}, {"start": 405.76, "end": 407.76, "text": " in devotional service of"}, {"start": 407.76, "end": 409.76, "text": " the Lord."}, {"start": 409.76, "end": 411.76, "text": " So, this is the meaning of"}, {"start": 411.76, "end": 413.76, "text": " we should actually"}, {"start": 413.76, "end": 415.76, "text": " depend upon the causeless"}, {"start": 415.76, "end": 417.76, "text": " mercy of the Lord and not on"}, {"start": 417.76, "end": 419.76, "text": " our own efforts alone."}, {"start": 419.76, "end": 421.76, "text": " However, this does"}, {"start": 421.76, "end": 423.76, "text": " not mean that"}, {"start": 423.76, "end": 425.76, "text": " I may do nothing"}, {"start": 425.76, "end": 427.76, "text": " and I simply think"}, {"start": 427.76, "end": 429.76, "text": " that whenever the Lord wants to give me"}, {"start": 429.76, "end": 431.76, "text": " darshan, he will give me."}, {"start": 431.76, "end": 433.76, "text": " Sometimes when we invite"}, {"start": 433.76, "end": 435.76, "text": " people to the temple,"}, {"start": 435.76, "end": 437.76, "text": " they tell,"}, {"start": 437.76, "end": 439.76, "text": " Jab Bhagwan bulayenge,"}, {"start": 439.76, "end": 441.76, "text": " hum ayenge."}, {"start": 441.76, "end": 443.76, "text": " Whenever the Lord wants me"}, {"start": 443.76, "end": 445.76, "text": " to come, I'll come."}, {"start": 445.76, "end": 447.76, "text": " Or whenever he invites me,"}, {"start": 447.76, "end": 449.76, "text": " I'll come."}, {"start": 449.76, "end": 451.76, "text": " Now, this is not the"}, {"start": 451.76, "end": 453.76, "text": " correct attitude."}, {"start": 453.76, "end": 455.76, "text": " If we don't take any"}, {"start": 455.76, "end": 457.76, "text": " step at all"}, {"start": 457.76, "end": 459.76, "text": " towards approaching"}, {"start": 459.76, "end": 461.76, "text": " the authorized process,"}, {"start": 461.76, "end": 463.76, "text": " then we'll never be able"}, {"start": 463.76, "end": 465.76, "text": " to see the Lord."}, {"start": 465.76, "end": 467.76, "text": " We'll never be able to approach the Lord."}, {"start": 467.76, "end": 469.76, "text": " This is very clear."}, {"start": 469.76, "end": 471.76, "text": " So, two things."}, {"start": 471.76, "end": 473.76, "text": " One is our own"}, {"start": 473.76, "end": 475.76, "text": " sincere efforts"}, {"start": 475.76, "end": 477.76, "text": " according to"}, {"start": 477.76, "end": 479.76, "text": " the scriptural"}, {"start": 479.76, "end": 481.76, "text": " direction, according to"}, {"start": 481.76, "end": 483.76, "text": " the instructions of the bona fide spiritual master,"}, {"start": 483.76, "end": 485.76, "text": " according to"}, {"start": 485.76, "end": 487.76, "text": " the process, authorized process"}, {"start": 487.76, "end": 489.76, "text": " that has to be there."}, {"start": 489.76, "end": 491.76, "text": " But this alone is not enough."}, {"start": 491.76, "end": 493.76, "text": " The second thing is"}, {"start": 493.76, "end": 495.76, "text": " the Lord's"}, {"start": 495.76, "end": 497.76, "text": " causeless mercy."}, {"start": 497.76, "end": 499.76, "text": " So that is being"}, {"start": 499.76, "end": 501.76, "text": " described here"}, {"start": 501.76, "end": 503.76, "text": " that we have to"}, {"start": 503.76, "end": 505.76, "text": " await the opportune moment."}, {"start": 505.76, "end": 507.76, "text": " We simply wait"}, {"start": 507.76, "end": 509.76, "text": " after doing whatever"}, {"start": 509.76, "end": 511.76, "text": " we have to do properly."}, {"start": 511.76, "end": 513.76, "text": " Narad Muni thought"}, {"start": 513.76, "end": 515.76, "text": " the Lord could be seen"}, {"start": 515.76, "end": 517.76, "text": " again by the same"}, {"start": 517.76, "end": 519.76, "text": " mechanical process"}, {"start": 519.76, "end": 521.76, "text": " that was successful"}, {"start": 521.76, "end": 523.76, "text": " in the first attempt."}, {"start": 523.76, "end": 525.76, "text": " But in spite of his"}, {"start": 525.76, "end": 527.76, "text": " utmost endeavor,"}, {"start": 527.76, "end": 529.76, "text": " he could not make"}, {"start": 529.76, "end": 531.76, "text": " the second attempt successful."}, {"start": 531.76, "end": 533.76, "text": " That was not possible."}, {"start": 533.76, "end": 535.76, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 535.76, "end": 537.76, "text": " Srila Prabhupada says"}, {"start": 537.76, "end": 539.76, "text": " the Lord is completely"}, {"start": 539.76, "end": 541.76, "text": " independent of all"}, {"start": 541.76, "end": 543.76, "text": " obligations."}, {"start": 543.76, "end": 545.76, "text": " But one important"}, {"start": 545.76, "end": 547.76, "text": " thing,"}, {"start": 547.76, "end": 549.76, "text": " the most important thing we should know"}, {"start": 549.76, "end": 551.76, "text": " about approaching the Lord"}, {"start": 551.76, "end": 553.76, "text": " or doing the"}, {"start": 553.76, "end": 555.76, "text": " devotional services,"}, {"start": 555.76, "end": 557.76, "text": " he can simply be bound up"}, {"start": 557.76, "end": 559.76, "text": " by the tie of"}, {"start": 559.76, "end": 561.76, "text": " unalloyed devotion."}, {"start": 561.76, "end": 563.76, "text": " One thing"}, {"start": 563.76, "end": 565.76, "text": " that Krishna"}, {"start": 565.76, "end": 567.76, "text": " really"}, {"start": 567.76, "end": 569.76, "text": " is completely"}, {"start": 569.76, "end": 571.76, "text": " thoroughly pleased"}, {"start": 571.76, "end": 573.76, "text": " when a devotee"}, {"start": 573.76, "end": 575.76, "text": " offers pure"}, {"start": 575.76, "end": 577.76, "text": " devotional service."}, {"start": 577.76, "end": 579.76, "text": " It is also called"}, {"start": 579.76, "end": 581.76, "text": " devotion unmixed"}, {"start": 581.76, "end": 583.76, "text": " with anything else."}, {"start": 583.76, "end": 585.76, "text": " Sent person"}, {"start": 585.76, "end": 587.76, "text": " pure devotional service."}, {"start": 587.76, "end": 589.76, "text": " Only that"}, {"start": 589.76, "end": 591.76, "text": " can actually bind the Lord"}, {"start": 591.76, "end": 593.76, "text": " because he agrees"}, {"start": 593.76, "end": 595.76, "text": " to become bound up."}, {"start": 595.76, "end": 597.76, "text": " Just like Mother Yashoda,"}, {"start": 597.76, "end": 599.76, "text": " she attempted to"}, {"start": 599.76, "end": 601.76, "text": " tie the Lord"}, {"start": 601.76, "end": 603.76, "text": " her child, whom she"}, {"start": 603.76, "end": 605.76, "text": " thought of as her beloved child"}, {"start": 605.76, "end": 607.76, "text": " when he was becoming little naughty."}, {"start": 607.76, "end": 609.76, "text": " She wanted to tie him"}, {"start": 609.76, "end": 611.76, "text": " to a grinding"}, {"start": 611.76, "end": 613.76, "text": " mortar with a rope."}, {"start": 613.76, "end": 615.76, "text": " She was"}, {"start": 615.76, "end": 617.76, "text": " trying and trying and trying"}, {"start": 617.76, "end": 619.76, "text": " and the rope was always"}, {"start": 619.76, "end": 621.76, "text": " falling short"}, {"start": 621.76, "end": 623.76, "text": " by two fingers."}, {"start": 623.76, "end": 625.76, "text": " That"}, {"start": 625.76, "end": 627.76, "text": " actually Krishna"}, {"start": 627.76, "end": 629.76, "text": " showed to us,"}, {"start": 629.76, "end": 631.76, "text": " it was for demonstrating to us,"}, {"start": 631.76, "end": 633.76, "text": " that he is not bound"}, {"start": 633.76, "end": 635.76, "text": " up simply because"}, {"start": 635.76, "end": 637.76, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 637.76, "end": 639.76, "text": " of some"}, {"start": 639.76, "end": 641.76, "text": " mother"}, {"start": 641.76, "end": 643.76, "text": " Yashoda catching him"}, {"start": 643.76, "end": 645.76, "text": " and binding and attempting"}, {"start": 645.76, "end": 647.76, "text": " to bind him with some rope."}, {"start": 647.76, "end": 649.76, "text": " She got all the rope available"}, {"start": 649.76, "end": 651.76, "text": " in her house"}, {"start": 651.76, "end": 653.76, "text": " but she was somehow not able to tie him."}, {"start": 653.76, "end": 655.76, "text": " And his form appeared"}, {"start": 655.76, "end": 657.76, "text": " only a limited form"}, {"start": 657.76, "end": 659.76, "text": " but we should know"}, {"start": 659.76, "end": 661.76, "text": " the Lord's form is unlimited"}, {"start": 661.76, "end": 663.76, "text": " and also"}, {"start": 663.76, "end": 665.76, "text": " one cannot bind him"}, {"start": 665.76, "end": 667.76, "text": " simply by"}, {"start": 667.76, "end": 669.76, "text": " some"}, {"start": 669.76, "end": 671.76, "text": " attempt of one's own."}, {"start": 671.76, "end": 673.76, "text": " The Lord should agree"}, {"start": 673.76, "end": 675.76, "text": " to become bound."}, {"start": 675.76, "end": 677.76, "text": " So after Mother Yashoda tried"}, {"start": 677.76, "end": 679.76, "text": " and tried and she became"}, {"start": 679.76, "end": 681.76, "text": " exhausted,"}, {"start": 681.76, "end": 683.76, "text": " then Krishna just smiled"}, {"start": 683.76, "end": 685.76, "text": " and immediately she was able to tie him."}, {"start": 687.76, "end": 689.76, "text": " So that is actually"}, {"start": 689.76, "end": 691.76, "text": " to also teach us that"}, {"start": 691.76, "end": 693.76, "text": " he agreed"}, {"start": 693.76, "end": 695.76, "text": " to become bound up"}, {"start": 695.76, "end": 697.76, "text": " by the love of Mother"}, {"start": 697.76, "end": 699.76, "text": " Yashoda. It is"}, {"start": 699.76, "end": 701.76, "text": " not ropes that can bind the Lord."}, {"start": 701.76, "end": 703.76, "text": " It is love that can bind the Lord."}, {"start": 703.76, "end": 705.76, "text": " And what kind of love is this?"}, {"start": 705.76, "end": 707.76, "text": " Love"}, {"start": 707.76, "end": 709.76, "text": " out of pure devotion."}, {"start": 709.76, "end": 711.76, "text": " That is what can"}, {"start": 711.76, "end": 713.76, "text": " bind the Lord."}, {"start": 715.76, "end": 717.76, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 717.76, "end": 719.76, "text": " he cannot be bound up simply"}, {"start": 719.76, "end": 721.76, "text": " by some"}, {"start": 721.76, "end": 723.76, "text": " material"}, {"start": 723.76, "end": 725.76, "text": " attempts. Similarly,"}, {"start": 725.76, "end": 727.76, "text": " the Lord is not visible"}, {"start": 727.76, "end": 729.76, "text": " or perceivable"}, {"start": 729.76, "end": 731.76, "text": " by our material senses."}, {"start": 737.76, "end": 739.76, "text": " Shastras clearly say"}, {"start": 739.76, "end": 741.76, "text": " material senses are totally"}, {"start": 741.76, "end": 743.76, "text": " incapable of"}, {"start": 743.76, "end": 745.76, "text": " actually perceiving"}, {"start": 745.76, "end": 747.76, "text": " the Lord."}, {"start": 747.76, "end": 749.76, "text": " Though,"}, {"start": 749.76, "end": 751.76, "text": " when he appears as an"}, {"start": 751.76, "end": 753.76, "text": " incarnation, he gives"}, {"start": 753.76, "end": 755.76, "text": " darshan even though he comes"}, {"start": 755.76, "end": 757.76, "text": " in his spiritual"}, {"start": 757.76, "end": 759.76, "text": " form and these eyes are"}, {"start": 759.76, "end": 761.76, "text": " useless for seeing spiritual form."}, {"start": 761.76, "end": 763.76, "text": " They are totally incapable of seeing"}, {"start": 763.76, "end": 765.76, "text": " any spiritual form. But still,"}, {"start": 765.76, "end": 767.76, "text": " he gives"}, {"start": 767.76, "end": 769.76, "text": " darshan to even"}, {"start": 769.76, "end": 771.76, "text": " people who have"}, {"start": 771.76, "end": 773.76, "text": " just got this ordinary vision."}, {"start": 773.76, "end": 775.76, "text": " He gives darshan."}, {"start": 775.76, "end": 777.76, "text": " That is his causeless mercy."}, {"start": 777.76, "end": 779.76, "text": " But people"}, {"start": 779.76, "end": 781.76, "text": " mistake him to be"}, {"start": 781.76, "end": 783.76, "text": " another created"}, {"start": 783.76, "end": 785.76, "text": " being of this world."}, {"start": 785.76, "end": 787.76, "text": " If he appears in a human-like"}, {"start": 787.76, "end": 789.76, "text": " form, as he appears when he"}, {"start": 789.76, "end": 791.76, "text": " appears as Krishna, then they think"}, {"start": 791.76, "end": 793.76, "text": " he is an ordinary covered boy or"}, {"start": 793.76, "end": 795.76, "text": " ordinary prince of"}, {"start": 795.76, "end": 797.76, "text": " this world, as son of Vasudeva."}, {"start": 797.76, "end": 799.76, "text": " As son of Nanda Maharaj,"}, {"start": 799.76, "end": 801.76, "text": " they think he is just an ordinary covered boy."}, {"start": 801.76, "end": 803.76, "text": " Or when he appears in the"}, {"start": 803.76, "end": 805.76, "text": " form of a fish or a tortoise"}, {"start": 805.76, "end": 807.76, "text": " or a boar,"}, {"start": 807.76, "end": 809.76, "text": " they think he is another"}, {"start": 809.76, "end": 811.76, "text": " and that creature is another"}, {"start": 811.76, "end": 813.76, "text": " boar or another fish"}, {"start": 813.76, "end": 815.76, "text": " of this world. No!"}, {"start": 815.76, "end": 817.76, "text": " He is completely"}, {"start": 817.76, "end": 819.76, "text": " spiritual and completely transient"}, {"start": 819.76, "end": 821.76, "text": " to everything material."}, {"start": 823.76, "end": 825.76, "text": " He may be seen"}, {"start": 825.76, "end": 827.76, "text": " out of his own accord"}, {"start": 827.76, "end": 829.76, "text": " when he gives"}, {"start": 829.76, "end": 831.76, "text": " darshan, when he gives"}, {"start": 831.76, "end": 833.76, "text": " vision to us."}, {"start": 833.76, "end": 835.76, "text": " Only then he can be seen."}, {"start": 835.76, "end": 837.76, "text": " And then in the 20th"}, {"start": 837.76, "end": 839.76, "text": " verse, it is said,"}, {"start": 839.76, "end": 841.76, "text": " evam yatantam vijane"}, {"start": 841.76, "end": 843.76, "text": " maam aha"}, {"start": 843.76, "end": 845.76, "text": " agochara giram"}, {"start": 845.76, "end": 847.76, "text": " gambhir shrakshanaya"}, {"start": 847.76, "end": 849.76, "text": " vaacha shuchap prashama"}, {"start": 849.76, "end": 851.76, "text": " yan iva"}, {"start": 851.76, "end": 853.76, "text": " Seeing my attempts"}, {"start": 853.76, "end": 855.76, "text": " in that lonely place,"}, {"start": 855.76, "end": 857.76, "text": " the personality of Godhead"}, {"start": 857.76, "end": 859.76, "text": " who is transcendental"}, {"start": 859.76, "end": 861.76, "text": " to all mundane description"}, {"start": 861.76, "end": 863.76, "text": " spoke to me with"}, {"start": 863.76, "end": 865.76, "text": " gravity and pleasing words"}, {"start": 865.76, "end": 867.76, "text": " just to mitigate my grief."}, {"start": 867.76, "end": 869.76, "text": " Krishna is very kind."}, {"start": 869.76, "end": 871.76, "text": " Even though"}, {"start": 871.76, "end": 873.76, "text": " he gave a brief darshan to Narada,"}, {"start": 873.76, "end": 875.76, "text": " still to mitigate"}, {"start": 875.76, "end": 877.76, "text": " Narada's grief"}, {"start": 877.76, "end": 879.76, "text": " because Narada was at grief,"}, {"start": 879.76, "end": 881.76, "text": " he was not able to see again."}, {"start": 881.76, "end": 883.76, "text": " Just to mitigate his grief,"}, {"start": 883.76, "end": 885.76, "text": " the Lord spoke to him."}, {"start": 887.76, "end": 889.76, "text": " Now, in the purport,"}, {"start": 889.76, "end": 891.76, "text": " Srila Prabhupada explains,"}, {"start": 891.76, "end": 893.76, "text": " in the Vedas it is said,"}, {"start": 893.76, "end": 895.76, "text": " God is beyond the approach"}, {"start": 895.76, "end": 897.76, "text": " of mundane words and intelligence."}, {"start": 897.76, "end": 899.76, "text": " avam manasa gochara"}, {"start": 899.76, "end": 901.76, "text": " Yet, by his causeless mercy,"}, {"start": 901.76, "end": 903.76, "text": " one can have suitable senses"}, {"start": 903.76, "end": 905.76, "text": " to hear him or to speak to him."}, {"start": 905.76, "end": 907.76, "text": " By his mercy,"}, {"start": 907.76, "end": 909.76, "text": " at the present moment,"}, {"start": 909.76, "end": 911.76, "text": " we are"}, {"start": 911.76, "end": 913.76, "text": " using our material senses"}, {"start": 913.76, "end": 915.76, "text": " to perceive"}, {"start": 915.76, "end": 917.76, "text": " material objects,"}, {"start": 917.76, "end": 919.76, "text": " but the completely spiritual"}, {"start": 919.76, "end": 921.76, "text": " form of the Lord"}, {"start": 921.76, "end": 923.76, "text": " or the spiritual sound"}, {"start": 923.76, "end": 925.76, "text": " of his transcendental vibration"}, {"start": 925.76, "end": 927.76, "text": " can be heard"}, {"start": 927.76, "end": 929.76, "text": " or can be seen"}, {"start": 929.76, "end": 931.76, "text": " by the Lord's mercy."}, {"start": 931.76, "end": 933.76, "text": " So, this is the Lord's"}, {"start": 933.76, "end": 935.76, "text": " inconceivable energy."}, {"start": 935.76, "end": 937.76, "text": " We cannot"}, {"start": 937.76, "end": 939.76, "text": " understand with"}, {"start": 939.76, "end": 941.76, "text": " our mundane logic."}, {"start": 941.76, "end": 943.76, "text": " The Lord was very pleased"}, {"start": 943.76, "end": 945.76, "text": " with Narada Muni"}, {"start": 945.76, "end": 947.76, "text": " and therefore,"}, {"start": 947.76, "end": 949.76, "text": " the necessary strength"}, {"start": 949.76, "end": 951.76, "text": " was invested in him"}, {"start": 951.76, "end": 953.76, "text": " so that Narada could hear the Lord."}, {"start": 953.76, "end": 955.76, "text": " It is not, however,"}, {"start": 955.76, "end": 957.76, "text": " possible for others"}, {"start": 957.76, "end": 959.76, "text": " to perceive directly"}, {"start": 959.76, "end": 961.76, "text": " the touch of the Lord"}, {"start": 961.76, "end": 963.76, "text": " during the probationary stage"}, {"start": 963.76, "end": 965.76, "text": " of regulative devotional service."}, {"start": 965.76, "end": 967.76, "text": " Those who are practicing"}, {"start": 967.76, "end": 969.76, "text": " in the probationary stage"}, {"start": 969.76, "end": 971.76, "text": " of regulative devotional service"}, {"start": 971.76, "end": 973.76, "text": " are said to be"}, {"start": 973.76, "end": 975.76, "text": " in the probationary stage"}, {"start": 975.76, "end": 977.76, "text": " of regulative devotional service."}, {"start": 977.76, "end": 979.76, "text": " That means,"}, {"start": 979.76, "end": 981.76, "text": " we are practicing."}, {"start": 981.76, "end": 983.76, "text": " It is also called sadhana bhakti,"}, {"start": 983.76, "end": 985.76, "text": " the stage of practice."}, {"start": 985.76, "end": 987.76, "text": " In the stage of practice,"}, {"start": 987.76, "end": 989.76, "text": " we are yet to reach the perfection."}, {"start": 989.76, "end": 991.76, "text": " Mind you,"}, {"start": 991.76, "end": 993.76, "text": " Narada had reached perfection."}, {"start": 993.76, "end": 995.76, "text": " But still,"}, {"start": 995.76, "end": 997.76, "text": " he had not yet"}, {"start": 997.76, "end": 999.76, "text": " become fully purified,"}, {"start": 999.76, "end": 1001.76, "text": " 100% purified,"}, {"start": 1001.76, "end": 1003.76, "text": " yet,"}, {"start": 1003.76, "end": 1005.76, "text": " though he was"}, {"start": 1005.76, "end": 1007.76, "text": " very sincerely following"}, {"start": 1007.76, "end": 1009.76, "text": " and had come to a"}, {"start": 1009.76, "end": 1011.76, "text": " stage of pretty good"}, {"start": 1011.76, "end": 1013.76, "text": " advancement stage."}, {"start": 1015.76, "end": 1017.76, "text": " So, when he heard"}, {"start": 1017.76, "end": 1019.76, "text": " the pleasing words of the Lord,"}, {"start": 1019.76, "end": 1021.76, "text": " the feelings of separation"}, {"start": 1021.76, "end": 1023.76, "text": " were to some extent mitigated."}, {"start": 1023.76, "end": 1025.76, "text": " A devotee in love"}, {"start": 1025.76, "end": 1027.76, "text": " feels always the pangs"}, {"start": 1027.76, "end": 1029.76, "text": " of separation,"}, {"start": 1029.76, "end": 1031.76, "text": " and is therefore"}, {"start": 1031.76, "end": 1033.76, "text": " always enwrapped"}, {"start": 1033.76, "end": 1035.76, "text": " in transcendental ecstasy."}, {"start": 1035.76, "end": 1037.76, "text": " Even hearing the Lord"}, {"start": 1037.76, "end": 1039.76, "text": " is in no way"}, {"start": 1039.76, "end": 1041.76, "text": " inferior"}, {"start": 1041.76, "end": 1043.76, "text": " to seeing the Lord"}, {"start": 1043.76, "end": 1045.76, "text": " or any other experience."}, {"start": 1045.76, "end": 1047.76, "text": " Though,"}, {"start": 1047.76, "end": 1049.76, "text": " we always desire"}, {"start": 1049.76, "end": 1051.76, "text": " if there is a person,"}, {"start": 1051.76, "end": 1053.76, "text": " we want to see him"}, {"start": 1053.76, "end": 1055.76, "text": " face to face."}, {"start": 1055.76, "end": 1057.76, "text": " We want to interact with him"}, {"start": 1057.76, "end": 1059.76, "text": " the way we interact with"}, {"start": 1059.76, "end": 1061.76, "text": " any person in this world."}, {"start": 1061.76, "end": 1063.76, "text": " Especially,"}, {"start": 1063.76, "end": 1065.76, "text": " dealings of love"}, {"start": 1065.76, "end": 1067.76, "text": " between two persons"}, {"start": 1067.76, "end": 1069.76, "text": " means there is"}, {"start": 1069.76, "end": 1071.76, "text": " active reciprocation."}, {"start": 1073.76, "end": 1075.76, "text": " I will stop here."}, {"start": 1075.76, "end": 1077.76, "text": " Thank you very much."}, {"start": 1077.76, "end": 1079.76, "text": " Hare Krishna."}]}